#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.random\\_integers"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:1 of
msgid "Random integers of type mt.int between `low` and `high`, inclusive."
msgstr "在 `low` 和 `high` 之间（包括两者）生成类型为 mt.int 的随机整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:3 of
msgid ""
"Return random integers of type mt.int from the \"discrete uniform\" "
"distribution in the closed interval [`low`, `high`].  If `high` is None "
"(the default), then results are from [1, `low`]. The np.int type "
"translates to the C long type used by Python 2 for \"short\" integers and"
" its precision is platform dependent."
msgstr ""
"从闭区间 [`low`, `high`] 内的“离散均匀”分布中返回类型为 mt.int 的随机"
"整数。如果 `high` 为 None（默认值），则结果来自 [1, `low`]。np.int 类型会"
"转换为 Python 2 中用于“短整数”的 C long 类型，其精度取决于平台。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:9 of
msgid "This function has been deprecated. Use randint instead."
msgstr "此函数已被弃用。请改用 randint。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:11 of
msgid ""
"Lowest (signed) integer to be drawn from the distribution (unless "
"``high=None``, in which case this parameter is the *highest* such "
"integer)."
msgstr ""
"从分布中抽取的最小（有符号）整数（除非 ``high=None``，在这种情况下此参数"
"是最大的此类整数）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:15 of
msgid ""
"If provided, the largest (signed) integer to be drawn from the "
"distribution (see above for behavior if ``high=None``)."
msgstr ""
"如果提供此参数，则是从分布中抽取的最大（有符号）整数（如果 ``high=None``"
"，请参见上文的行为说明）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:18 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  Default is None, in which case a single value is"
" returned."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。默认值为 None，这种情况下返回单个值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:22 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:24 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:27 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- `size`-shaped array of random integers from the appropriate "
"distribution, or a single such random int if `size` not provided."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 来自适当分布的 `size` 形状的随机整数数组，如果未提供 `size`，"
"则返回单个这样的随机整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`random.randint`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:34 of
msgid ""
"Similar to `random_integers`, only for the half-open interval [`low`, "
"`high`), and 0 is the lowest value if `high` is omitted."
msgstr ""
"与 `random_integers` 类似，但用于半开区间 [`low`, `high`)，如果省略 `high"
"`，则 0 是最小值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.random_integers.random_integers:37 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

